A fan collection of custom poems I typewritten for my followers throughout the years.
 
Each poem was photographed from their liking, while the poem was based on their topic. 

If able, feel free to click on the poem to either make an offer or buy outright the ownership of the digital poem.

~If you want your appletreepoetry poem turned into a free NFT, DM me on instagram @appletreepoetry. Furthermore, if you desire a custom poem, visit my website at www.appletreepoetry.com.~
